  "date": "2026-01-26",
  "notes": "<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Corruption\nRisk Mapping<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Interview\nReport<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0cm\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\nline-height:115%\">&nbsp;</span></b></p>\n\n<table class=\"MsoNormalTable\" border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\">\n <tbody><tr>\n  <td width=\"148\" style=\"width:111.15pt;border:solid #E6E6E6 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:\n  solid #E6E6E6 .75pt;background:whitesmoke;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;color:black;mso-color-alt:windowtext\">Item</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n  </td>\n  <td width=\"515\" style=\"width:386.1pt;border:solid #E6E6E6 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:\n  solid #E6E6E6 .75pt;background:whitesmoke;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;color:black;mso-color-alt:windowtext\">Information</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n  </td>\n </tr>\n <tr>\n  <td width=\"148\" style=\"width:111.15pt;border:solid #E6E6E6 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:\n  solid #E6E6E6 .75pt;background:whitesmoke;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;color:black;mso-color-alt:windowtext\">Date\n  of the interview</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n  </td>\n  <td width=\"515\" style=\"width:386.1pt;border:solid #E6E6E6 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:\n  solid #E6E6E6 .75pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">26 January 2026<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n  </td>\n </tr>\n <tr>\n  <td width=\"148\" style=\"width:111.15pt;border:solid #E6E6E6 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:\n  solid #E6E6E6 .75pt;background:whitesmoke;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;color:black;mso-color-alt:windowtext\">Interviewee</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n  </td>\n  <td width=\"515\" style=\"width:386.1pt;border:solid #E6E6E6 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:\n  solid #E6E6E6 .75pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Pilar MARTINEZ<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n  </td>\n </tr>\n <tr>\n  <td width=\"148\" style=\"width:111.15pt;border:solid #E6E6E6 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:\n  solid #E6E6E6 .75pt;background:whitesmoke;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;color:black;mso-color-alt:windowtext\">Position</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n  </td>\n  <td width=\"515\" style=\"width:386.1pt;border:solid #E6E6E6 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:\n  solid #E6E6E6 .75pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Representative\n  of Excelsia – coordination of all LFB Spain operational functions<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n  </td>\n </tr>\n <tr>\n  <td width=\"148\" style=\"width:111.15pt;border:solid #E6E6E6 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:\n  solid #E6E6E6 .75pt;background:whitesmoke;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;color:black;mso-color-alt:windowtext\">Interviewers</span></b><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n  </td>\n  <td width=\"515\" style=\"width:386.1pt;border:solid #E6E6E6 1.0pt;mso-border-alt:\n  solid #E6E6E6 .75pt;padding:.75pt .75pt .75pt .75pt\">\n  <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Sandra LASAGNI, Sandra LEZMI<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n  </td>\n </tr>\n</tbody></table>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;color:#0070C0;mso-ansi-language:\nEN-US\">1. Scope of responsibilities and activities<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Department and organisational\nperimeter<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n\n<ul type=\"disc\">\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Work\n     through <b>Excelsia</b>, the company responsible for <b>coordinating all\n     operational functions</b> for LFB in Spain, covering:<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <ul type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Commercial\n      activities (Key Account Managers)<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Marketing support<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Medical\n      support (MSL / Medical Affairs)<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Warehouse &amp; logistics\n      coordination<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Accounting support<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Legal &amp; compliance support<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Management\n      of external law firms and regulatory topics<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n </ul>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Excelsia\n     coordinates <b>all daily operations</b> on behalf of <b>LFB Bioterapias\n     España</b>, in close alignment with <b>LFB Biomedicament (Group)</b>.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Team and geographic scope<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n\n<ul type=\"disc\">\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:\n     11.0pt;line-height:115%\">LFB Spain has: <o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <ul type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">3 Key Account Managers</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">1 marketing support</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">1 medical support</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Additional\n      operational functions contributed via Excelsia<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n </ul>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Geographic\n     perimeter: <b>Spain (national coverage)</b><o:p></o:p></span></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Main missions and objectives<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n\n<ul type=\"disc\">\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:\n     11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Commercial &amp; promotion activities</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">:<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <ul type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Visits\n      to hospital physicians and pharmacists by KAMs<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Scientific\n      visits by MSLs (including out‑of‑label or publication‑focused discussions\n      when permitted)<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Combined\n      KAM + MSL visits for clinical study presentations<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Organisation of: <o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <ul type=\"square\">\n   <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Staff meetings<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n   <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Clinical sessions<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n   <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Advisory\n       boards (strictly medical only)<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  </ul>\n </ul>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:\n     11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Market access &amp; contracting strategy</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <ul type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">LFB\n      Spain currently <b>does not respond to public tenders</b> due to supply\n      constraints and risk of not meeting contractually binding volumes.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Instead,\n      LFB negotiates <b>direct individual contracts</b> with hospitals for\n      flexible pricing and quantities.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Plan to\n      <b>restart tender applications from 2027</b>, once supply stabilises.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n </ul>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:\n     11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Supply chain &amp; logistics</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <ul type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Coordination\n      with <b>UPS</b> (formerly Bomi/Ecco Pharma) for: <o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <ul type=\"square\">\n   <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Importation<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n   <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Storage<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n   <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Preparation of orders<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n   <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Distribution to hospitals<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  </ul>\n </ul>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:\n     11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Regulatory, compliance, finance &amp; legal</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <ul type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Coordination\n      with the law firm for contract review, tax matters, and process\n      optimisation.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Responsibility\n      for ensuring compliance with: <o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <ul type=\"square\">\n   <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">LFB internal anti‑corruption\n       policies<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n   <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:\n       EN-US\">Farmaindustria Code</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:\n       11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\"> (mandatory in Spain)<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n   <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Voluntary alignment with EFPIA\n       standards<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  </ul>\n </ul>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Training\n     &amp; ethics: </span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\n     line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">all employees must: <o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <ul type=\"circle\">\n  <ul type=\"square\">\n   <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Receive,\n       read and sign the LFB Code of Conduct upon joining.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n   <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Attend\n       regular refresh sessions during sales meetings.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  </ul>\n </ul>\n</ul>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;color:#0070C0;mso-ansi-language:\nEN-US\">2. Third parties, nature of interactions, corruption risks and controls<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">2.1. Public Hospitals (≈95–98% of\nactivity)<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n\n<ul type=\"disc\">\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:\n     11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Nature of interactions</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <ul type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Negotiation\n      of <b>direct purchase contracts</b> outside public tenders due to market\n      shortages.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Hospitals\n      often engage <b>multiple suppliers</b> for albumin and immunoglobulins.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">For\n      coagulation factors, tenders normally apply, but LFB does not participate\n      currently.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n </ul>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:\n     11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Frequency &amp; business volume</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <ul type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Core\n      business channel in Spain.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Continuous\n      ordering depending on patient needs.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n </ul>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Corruption\n     risks are very low</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\n     line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\"> because: <o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <ul type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Public\n      procurement is <b>highly regulated</b>.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Procedures\n      are <b>transparent</b> and documents are publicly accessible.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Prices\n      can be officially requested from hospitals.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n </ul>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:\n     11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Controls identified</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <ul type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Legal\n      framework of the Spanish public contracting system.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Transparency\n      of offers and awards.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Multiplicity\n      of decision‑makers reduces discretionary risk.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n </ul>\n</ul>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">2.2. Private Hospitals (≈2–5% of\nactivity)<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n\n<ul type=\"disc\">\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:\n     11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Nature of interactions</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <ul type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Mainly one hospital: <b>Clinica\n      Universitaria de Navarra</b>.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Agreement based on: <o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <ul type=\"square\">\n   <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Discussion\n       with pharmacist + economic department.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n   <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Offer (product + price).<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n   <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Acceptance\n       by signed offer or first purchase order.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  </ul>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Relationship\n      based on LFB <b>general terms and conditions of sale</b>.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n </ul>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">No\n     specific corruption risks identified: </span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">hospital\n     is financially sound and reputed.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:\n     11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Controls mentioned</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <ul type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Prior\n      financial assessment of the private hospital.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Formal acceptance of offers.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n </ul>\n</ul>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">2.3. Healthcare Professionals (HCPs)<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n\n<ul type=\"disc\">\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:\n     11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Nature of interactions</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <ul type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Scientific promotion.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Congress\n      sponsorship (upon formal request letter).<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Fee-for-service\n      engagements (presentations, advisory boards).<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Strict\n      application of Farmaindustria Code.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n </ul>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:\n     11.0pt;line-height:115%\">FMV determination</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <ul type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Benchmark against: <o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <ul type=\"square\">\n   <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Competitors\n       in plasma derivatives (Octapharma, Takeda, Grifols…)<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n   <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Other\n       pharma companies (GSK, Sanofi…)<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n   <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Information directly from HCPs<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  </ul>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Standardised\n      working time: typically 3–4 hours preparation + 1 hour delivery.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n </ul>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:\n     11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Corruption risks mentioned</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <ul type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Pressure\n      from some HCPs requesting higher fees (especially compared to large\n      companies).<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Historically\n      (20–30 years ago) HCPs used to ask for benefits (spa, entertainment), but\n      not anymore.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n </ul>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:\n     11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Controls mentioned</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <ul type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Strict\n      adherence to Farmaindustria Code with strict rules applies:<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <ul type=\"square\">\n   <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Only event duration covered.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n   <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">No accompanying persons.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n   <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">No 5‑star\n       hotels; capped prices defined.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n   <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Additional\n       night only for logistic reasons.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  </ul>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Internal\n      contracting for each activity with fixed hours.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Three-level\n      internal validation (requester/reviewer/approver).<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Regular training.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n </ul>\n</ul>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">2.4.\nSuppliers and Service Providers<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Travel\nagency<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n\n<ul type=\"disc\">\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Selected\n     from 3 candidates; reviewed every <b>2–3 years</b>.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Mandatory\n     use for Employee travel and HCP travel (sponsorship)<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Travel\n     rules: Train preferred, economy class<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Theorical\n     corruption risks</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\n     line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">: gifts/invitations from agency<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Controls</span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:\n     EN-US\">: refusal of gifts &gt; €6; contract with service levels; periodic\n     review.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">IT suppliers<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n\n<ul type=\"disc\">\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Group\n     policy: <b>Dell only</b>, including model selection.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:\n     11.0pt;line-height:115%\">No local discretion; reduces risk.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\npage-break-after:avoid\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Telecom\nproviders<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n\n<ul type=\"disc\">\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Selected\n     among the <b>3 major national operators</b>.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Marketing agencies<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n\n<ul type=\"disc\">\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Small\n     specialised agencies used for materials, printing, videos.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:\n     11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Engagement based on quotes/contracts.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:\n     11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Segregation of duties applied.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Logistician (UPS)<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n\n<ul type=\"disc\">\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Tripartite\n     Master Service Agreement (LFB Group + LFB Spain + UPS).<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Contract\n     terms validated by the Group.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Regulatory\n/ Medical information / PV partner <o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:\nauto;mso-add-space:auto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l7 level1 lfo16\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:Symbol;\nmso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;mso-ansi-language:\nEN-US;mso-bidi-font-weight:bold\">·<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\nline-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Regulatory and safety services\nprovided by QBD<b><o:p></o:p></b></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Legal advisors <o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:\nauto;mso-add-space:auto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l13 level1 lfo15\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:Symbol;\nmso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;mso-ansi-language:\nEN-US\">·<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\nline-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Local law firm for contractual, tax\nand legal support<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Accounting &amp; labour provider<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"mso-margin-top-alt:auto;mso-margin-bottom-alt:\nauto;mso-add-space:auto;text-indent:-18.0pt;mso-list:l13 level1 lfo15\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;font-family:Symbol;\nmso-fareast-font-family:Symbol;mso-bidi-font-family:Symbol;mso-ansi-language:\nEN-US\">·<span style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n</span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\nline-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Outsourced accounting and HR services\nto Soreco<o:p></o:p></span></p>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Excelsia<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n\n<ul type=\"disc\">\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Acts as\n     an operational extension of LFB Spain.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Required\n     to follow LFB compliance rules.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:\n     11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Subject to internal audits.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Corruption\n     risks very low </span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\n     line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">because:<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <ul type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">No\n      supplier attempts at offering gifts.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Strong\n      emphasis on refusal of any advantage.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n </ul>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:\n     11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Controls mentioned</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <ul type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Contractualisation.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Segregation of duties.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Group‑level supplier\n      references.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Compliance audits.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n </ul>\n</ul>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">2.5. Authorities and Public Bodies<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n\n<ul type=\"disc\">\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Frequent\n     interactions with regional health authorities and Ministry of Health.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">All\n     processes are <b>public</b> and involve <b>multiple institutional\n     interlocutors</b>.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">No corruption\n     risks </span></b><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:\n     115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">perceived due to transparency and collective\n     decision‑making.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:\n     11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Controls mentioned</span></b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\"> <o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <ul type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Prohibition\n      of individual informal meetings.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">Structured, documented\n      exchanges.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n </ul>\n</ul>\n\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%\">2.6. Conflicts of Interest<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\n\n<ul type=\"disc\">\n <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">No known\n     existing conflicts of interest. </span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\n     line-height:115%\">If one arises: <o:p></o:p></span></li>\n <ul type=\"circle\">\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Must be\n      escalated to management (e.g., Javier).<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n  <li class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"font-size:11.0pt;line-height:115%;mso-ansi-language:EN-US\">Decision-maker\n      replaced if necessary.<o:p></o:p></span></li>\n </ul>\n</ul>",
